('PS5 Game - Spider-Man 2 Collector''s Edition', 1329900, 'Games', 'The Spider-Men, Peter Parker and Miles Morales, return in a thrilling adventure in the critically acclaimed Marvel''s Spider-Man franchise for PS5. Quickly switch between Peter Parker and Miles Morales to experience different storylines and epic new powers, as the iconic villain Venom threatens to destroy their lives, their city and their loved ones - get yours now and collect it!', 'https://i.imgur.com/Al38auX.png', 20, 0.00),
('Funko Pop - Spider-Man', 119000, 'Figures', 'Bring home the friendly neighbour Spider-Man with this awesome Funko Pop! With his iconic costume and dynamic pose, this collectible figure is perfect for fans of all ages. Whether you put it on your shelf or give it as a gift to a loved one, this Spider-Man Funko Pop is sure to bring a smile to anyone''s face!', 'https://i.imgur.com/lQt6BVb.png', 30, 0.12),
('XBOX Series X Console - 1TB + Wireless Control', 3389900, 'Consoles', 'Want the best gaming experience possible? Then you need the XBOX X Series, the most powerful, fastest and most compatible console ever. Enjoy stunning graphics, minimal loading times and a huge library of games from four generations. And with the storage expansion card, you''ll never run out of space for your favourite games. So don''t wait any longer and get the XBOX X Series, the console that has it all.', 'https://i.imgur.com/6HusjTo.png', 25, 0.20),
