('XBOX Series X Game - Marvel''s Guardians Of The Galaxy', 319900, 'Games', 'Do you like space adventures, humour and 80s music? Then don''t miss Guardians of the Galaxy, the new Marvel game that puts you in the role of Star-Lord, the leader of a group of crazy heroes. Explore incredible worlds, face epic villains and enjoy a soundtrack that will make you dance - order your copy now and live a galactic experience!', 'https://i.imgur.com/oBhBglw.png', 12, 0.00),
('XBOX ONE Game - Star Wars Jedi Fallen Order', 249900, 'Games', 'Would you like to live a galactic adventure as a true Jedi? With the XBOX ONE Star Wars Jedi Fallen Order game, you can explore incredible worlds, face challenging enemies and use your lightsaber and Force powers to overcome obstacles. Enjoy immersive, cinematic combat and an original story that will make you feel part of the Star Wars universe - don''t miss this chance to become the hero you''ve always dreamed of!', 'https://i.imgur.com/VucKEj3.png', 15, 0.15),
('Funko Pop - Darth Vader', 119000, 'Figures', 'Complete your Star Wars collection with this Funko Pop figure of Darth Vader. This collectible is perfect for fans of the saga and features Darth Vader, the dreaded Sith Lord and one of the most iconic characters in film history. The figure captures the iconic details of Darth Vader''s helmet and armour, and is an ideal gift for any Star Wars fan.', 'https://i.imgur.com/SWBtsVT.png', 8, 0.12);
